quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  2,283,"Si on ngonii e …óatngal on ke…ďaani binndoowo tottirre jukunnde tamaande, si on koolandirii, oon tottaa…óo hoolaare yo tottit hoolaare nde, yo o hul Alla joom makko, wotee cuu…óe seedanfaagu kala cuu…óo ngu pellet oon …ďernde makko ko bakkadinnde, Alla na anndi ko ngollaton ko"
  2,284,"Woodanii Alla ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi si on …ďannginii ko e pittaali mon wolla on cuu…ói ma Alla haasbu mon sabu mum, O yaafoo mbo O wela O lepta mbo wela, Alla ko kattan…óo kala huunde"
  2,285,"Nulaa…óo goon…óanii ko jippinaa ko e Makko ummade e Joom Makko, e goonin…ďe …ďe fof …ďe goon…óanii Alla e malaykaaji Makko e defte makko e Nulaa…ďe makko, min ceerndatah hay gooto e Nulaa…ďe makko, …ďe wii min nanii min …óoftiima hafran amen Joomi amen ko Mah woni ruttorde"
  2,286,"Alla fawatah fittaandu kondu hattanaani,woodanii ndu kondu faggii, fawiima e dow mayru kondu faggitii,Joomi amen woto nanngir min ko min njjiti ko wollo ko min ngoopi ko,woto A faw e amen tampere hono no ndoondirna…óa …ďeen adii…ďe amen,Joomi amen woto faw min komin kattanaani,yaafa amin cuura bakkatuuJi amen nJurma…óa min ko Aan woni keeda amin wollu min e dow yim…ďe heeferee…ďe …ďe"
  3,1,"Alif, Laam, Miim"
  3,2,"Alla: rewetee…óo woo alaa si wanaa KaŇčko. Ko O Wuur…óo, √Ďii…ďu…óo"
  3,3,"O Jippinirii Deftere nden dow maa…óa e goonga, goonginnde ko adii nde, O Jippini Tawreeta e Linnjiila"
  3,4,"Ko adii, fii fewnugol yim…ďe …ďen, O Jippini AlQur'aana. Pellet yeddu…ďe Aayeeje Alla …óen, hino woodani …ďe lepte sa…ótu…óe. Alla Ko Foolu…óo, Jom-yottagol"
  3,5,"Pellet, Alla, huunde suu…óotaako Mo ka leydi wanaa ka kammu"
  3,6,"Ko KaŇčko Woni Mbaadiniroowo on ka renngaaji noone woo no O Muuyiri. Rewetee…óo woo alaa si wanaa KaŇčko, Foolu…óo, √Ďee√Īu…óo"
  3,7,"Ko KaŇčko Woni Jippin…óo Deftere nden e maa…óa, no e mayre aayeeje …ďaŇčngu…óe; ko kaŇčje woni neene Deftere nden, e go…ó…óe goo nanndu…óe. Ammaa …ďen …ďe oo√Īaare woni e nder …ďer…óe mun, hi…ďe jokka ko nanndi kon e majje …óa…ď…ďugol fitina e …óa…ďugol firtugol …óe. Anndataa firo majje si wanaa Alla. Tutii…ďe …ďen e ganndal no wi'a: \"Men gom…óinii nde, kala mun ko immorde ka Joomi amen\". Waajitotaako si wanaa joomiraa…ďe haqqillaaji …ďen"
  3,8,"joomi amen, wata oo√Īu …ďer…óe amen …óen …ďaawo nde fewnu-…óaa men, ye…óu men yurmeende immorde ka Maa…óa.Pellet An, ko An Woni Ye…óoowo=dokko"
  3,9,"Joomi amen, pellet An ko A Moo…ďoyoowo yim…ďe …ďen √Īalnde nde sikke alah e mun Pellet Alla luutintaa fodoore nden"
  3,10,"Pellet …ďen yeddu…ďe, jawle ma…ď…ďe e …ďi…ó…ďe ma…ď…ďe duncaŇčtaa…ďe e lepte Alla …óen hay e huunde. Ko …ďen woni carmale yiite ngen"
  3,11,"Wano mbowdi yim…ďe Fir'awna e …ďen adinoo…ďe …ďe. ∆Āe fennii aayeeje Amen …óen, Alla Nanngitiri …ďe junubaaji ma…ď…ďe …óin. Alla ko Sa…ótu…óo lepte"
  3,12,"Maakan …ďen yeddu…ďe: \"On fooloyte moo…ďoye-…óon ka jahannama\". Nge bonii nda…ó…óudi"
  3,13,"Gom…óii laatanike on aaya e …óin feddeejji …ói…ói fottu…ói fiiha…ďugol: fedde goo no ha…ďa e laawol Alla, wonnde goo ko yeddunde, hi…ďe yi'ira…ďe yeru ma…ď…ďe laaw…ďi …ói…ói gii…óe gite. Alla no Semmbinira balla Makko ngal o Mo O Muuyi. Pellet, no e …óum waaju wonannde joomiraa…ďe-haqqillaaji"
  3,14,"Yim…ďe …ďen cu…óinanaama yi…óugol tuuyooji: immorde e rew…ďe e …ďi…ó…ďe wor…ďe, e jawle tuginidiraa…óe, immorde e kaŇčŇče e kaalise, e pucci Ňčar…ói…óaa…ói, e neemoraa…ói, e remuru. ∆äum …óon, ko dakamme nguurdam aduna. Alla, no ka Makko mo∆ī∆īu…óum ruttorde"